{"tid":1534522,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"要養成買野前先睇清楚係咪中國製既習慣","createTime":"2019-09-03T04:33:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T04:50:54.000Z","uid":12609,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0f5f16a079068bbf050259c7d98f24eabda59229","tid":1534522,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:33:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sVzXSE6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsVzXSE6.jpg&h=e35bbee7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你每買一件中國製既貨品<br />\n都係資助緊中共打壓香港<br />\n買任何野前睇清楚係唔係MADE IN CHINA<br />\n一定要杯葛MADE IN CHINA"},{"pid":"3ef274b0265f9b5a6e8c19a3e2b3e3f6d889ea56","tid":1534522,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:34:22.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f09c5c4d316e68234c11e30e061deb027e420b8","tid":1534522,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:35:23.000Z","msg":"明白大家呢排嘅士氣經過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831恐襲</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">901大撤退</span></span>之後好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同大家一樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但越係呢啲時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地就越要堅持下去，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">團結一致</span></span><br />\n唔好比林鄭見我地冇士氣而去捉多啲人<br />\n<br />\n以下兩篇文章<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>，定係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n<br />\n灰心喪志，是因為你看不見抗爭的前路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533741</a>"},{"pid":"63013a4cd9a20ed5f045ed862433d76055fdc533","tid":1534522,"uid":57554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:38:22.000Z","msg":"而家仲有中國制咩? <br />\nD 廠走得 7788 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b351e567b0ea1fae31434b4827c27a5736d556c","tid":1534522,"uid":98926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:40:05.000Z","msg":"[法律] [一石二鳥] 教你點攞法庭命令迫黨鐵交太子站CCTV 再告埋香港警察同港鐵！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1534194\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1534194</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">有冇人識831太子車廂嘅人 佢哋出嚟先可以拎CCTV 睇下有冇人死</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n個撚個話關心義士 去太子送花<br />\n<strong><span